#

Beet and Carrot Borscht

60 min
$10
150 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Soup

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodHealthy

Description

A vibrant and warm soup that combines earthy beets and sweet carrots, perfect for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • beets: 2 medium, peeled and grated
  • carrots: 2 medium, peeled and grated
  • onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • potatoes: 2 medium, diced
  • vegetable broth: 6 cups
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • sour cream: for serving
  • fresh dill: for garnish
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • bay leaves: 2
